title: Episode 65: Camp Lloyd with Dr. Illene Cupit
itunes:author: UW-Green Bay Psychology Department
itunes:summary: In this new episode, host Dr. Ryan Martin is joined by Dr. Illene Cupit and students Taylor Gulbrand and Hannah Roffers. Throughout the episode, they share information and experiences surrounding Camp Lloyd. Camp Lloyd is a day camp for children grieving the loss of a loved one, where they learn the normality of grief and have a fun week with peers!
